ghly the reasoning that SBF himself used in buying=C2=A0<em>other=C2=A0</em=
>busted crypto firms earlier this year: =E2=80=9CThe explicit working princ=
iple we had,=E2=80=9D <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/cl=
ick/29719674.276531/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzI=
