s okay to do a deal that is moderately bad =E2=80=A6=C2=A0like, we are inci=
nerating a relatively small-ish amount of money in doing this,=E2=80=9D in =
order to keep the crypto ecosystem healthy and =E2=80=9Cbe a good construct=
