ing about=C2=A0<em>that=C2=A0</em>balance sheet. But it would be quite some=
thing if he did.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Elsewhere, <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomb=
ergbusiness.com/click/29719674.276531/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cucmV1dGVycy5jb20vdGVja=
G5vbG9neS9mdHhzLWJhbmttYW4tZnJpZWQtYmVnZ2VkLXJlc2N1ZS1ldmVuLWhlLXJldmVhbGVk=
