er-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: so=
lid; background-color: #ccc;">some bad news on the sex and drugs front</a>:=
</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Since FTX=E2=80=99s collapse, rumors have spre=
ad on Twitter that many FTX employees took prescription stimulants, includi=
ng Adderall, to enhance their productivity and work longer hours.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But Dr. Lerner disputed that characterization.=
 He said that some FTX employees may have been given prescription medicatio=
ns to treat A.D.H.D., but that the =E2=80=9Crate of A.D.H.D. in the company=
 was in line with most tech companies.=E2=80=9D He said that he wrote some =
prescriptions to FTX employees, but only those he treated as part of his pe=
rsonal practice.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Details about the romantic pairings reported b=
y CoinDesk last week led some gossips on Twitter to dub FTX a =E2=80=9Cpoly=
cule,=E2=80=9D a term for a web of non-monogamous relationships.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But Dr. Lerner rejected that idea, saying the =
company=E2=80=99s culture was far from orgiastic.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CIt=E2=80=99s a pretty tame place,=E2=
=80=9D Dr. Lerner said. =E2=80=9CThe higher-ups, they mostly played chess a=
nd board games. There was no partying. They were undersexed, if anything.=
=E2=80=9D</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">So probably not=C2=A0<em>Wolf of Wall Street</=
em>. Still, that=E2=80=99s fine. I recently re-watched=C2=A0<em>Margin Call=
</em>, the best finance movie, and you could see this working in that genre=
. The dramatic moments are not the drug-fueled orgies but the moment when t=
he junior analyst notices the backdoor in the spreadsheet. I would watch th=
at kind of movie.</p>
